course_aims:
This course aims to develop entrepreneurs and entrepreneurship by introducing students to the theory, practice and research needed to start and grow new ventures. It aims to;

Teach students how to match types of ventures to entrepreneurial goals;

Design innovative business models to both deliver and capture value;

Assess market attractiveness;

Create competitive advantage through the formation of a venture; and

Present ideas in a compelling manner via presentation/pitch sessions and the production of a written business proposal.
